  "title": "Direct Sales & Marketing Representative",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Direct Sales and Marketing Representative </strong></em></p><p><u>Ascend Marketing Solutions</u><br />Ascend Marketing Solutions is a performance-driven sales and marketing firm specializing in direct customer acquisition and brand development. The company partners with national and regional clients to deliver face-to-face marketing strategies designed to increase market share, strengthen brand presence, and drive measurable growth. Ascend Marketing Solutions emphasizes professionalism, accountability, and results, while providing structured training and opportunities for career development.</p><p><u>Position Overview</u><br />The Direct Sales and Marketing Representative is responsible for executing face-to-face sales and marketing initiatives that drive customer acquisition and revenue growth. This role represents Ascend Marketing Solutions in a professional manner while supporting strategic sales objectives and enhancing brand visibility.</p><p><u>Key Responsibilities</u><br />Execute direct sales and marketing campaigns to acquire new customers, communicate product value and brand messaging effectively, build and maintain professional customer relationships, meet or exceed assigned sales performance targets, maintain accurate reporting of sales activities, and collaborate with internal teams to support campaign goals.</p><p><u>Qualifications</u><br />Prior experience in sales, marketing, or customer-facing roles is preferred, along with strong communication and interpersonal skills, a professional demeanor, a results-driven mindset, and the ability to work both independently and collaboratively within a team.</p>",
